---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="About">
  <section class="container" style="padding: var(--space-lg) var(--space-md); max-width: 720px;">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p>
      Sowthri · GenAI Architect · based in Dammam, Saudi Arabia.
    </p>
    <p style="margin-top: var(--space-sm);">
      This portfolio demonstrates end-to-end architectural capability for Industrial AI in Refining, Petrochemicals, Utilities, and Mining. Every project ships with infrastructure-as-code, observability, safety guardrails, tests across seven tiers, and a full TCO reconciliation.
    </p>
    <h2>Approach</h2>
    <p>
      Platform before payload. Production-ready in design · portfolio-economical in operation. Deliberate failure branches so reviewers see the gates actually firing. Full public source across two GitHub repositories — nothing private · nothing hidden.
    </p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      <a href="https://github.com/sowthri-industrial-ai">GitHub: sowthri-industrial-ai</a>
    </p>
  </section>
</Base>
